name: 3 Count Bout
desc: 3 Count Bout is a wrestling game where the player can choose from 10 different wrestlers and compete in various matches, including ring matches, street matches, and death matches, to become the world champion of the SNK Wrestling Federation

name: Alpha Mission II
desc: Alpha Mission II is a shoot 'em up game where the player controls a space fighter to stop the Seven Star Alliance, led by a giant android, from invading Earth.

name: Andro Dunos
desc: Andro Dunos is a side-scrolling shoot 'em up game where players control a new type of space fighter craft to end a long war against an alien invasion.

name: Art of Fighting 3: The Path of the Warrior
Double Dragon
desc: Double Dragon is a beat 'em up game that follows the Lee brothers, Billy and Jimmy, who must rescue Billy’s girlfriend Marian from the clutches of the Black Warriors gang, led by the mysterious Shadow Boss.

name: Far East of Eden: Kabuki Klash
Fatal Fury 3: Road to the Final Victory
Metal Slug
desc: Metal Slug is a classic arcade game that follows the adventures of a group of elite soldiers who fight against the evil General Morden and his rebel army, who plan to use a powerful weapon called the Metal Slug to conquer the world.

name: Metal Slug 2
desc: Metal Slug 2 is a run and gun game that follows the Peregrine Falcon Squad, who team up with the Rebel Army to stop General Morden’s alliance with the Mars People, who have betrayed him and plan to invade Earth.

name: Metal Slug 3
desc: Metal Slug 3 is a run and gun game that follows the Peregrine Falcon Squad, who must stop General Morden’s second coup attempt, which is aided by a mysterious alien race called the Invaders, who have their own agenda.

name: Metal Slug 4
desc: Metal Slug 4 is a run and gun game that follows the special-opts PF Squad, who must stop the cyber terrorist group Amadeus from unleashing a deadly virus that can control military systems across the world.

name: Metal Slug 5
desc: Metal Slug 5 is a run and gun game that follows the special-ops PF Squad, who must stop the Ptolemaic Army, a secret cult that has stolen the Metal Slug data and plans to use it for world domination.

name: Metal Slug X
desc: Metal Slug X is a run and gun game that follows the Peregrine Falcon Squad, who must stop General Morden’s third coup attempt, which is complicated by the appearance of a time portal that brings enemies from different eras.

name: Minna-san no Okage-sama Desu! Dai Sugoroku Taikai
Neo Geo Cup '98: The Road to the Victory
Puzzle Bobble
desc: Bust-A-Move is a puzzle game where you control a pointer at the bottom of the screen and shoot colored bubbles to match and pop them before they reach the bottom.

name: Quiz Daisōsasen: The Last Count Down
Quiz Meitantei Neo & Geo: Quiz Daisōsasen Part 2
Real Bout Fatal Fury 2: The Newcomers
Samurai Shodown III: Blades of Blood
Sengoku
desc: Sengoku is a beat 'em up game where the player controls a ninja or a cowboy who must fight against the undead forces of a resurrected warlord who wants to conquer the world.

name: Shōgi no Tatsujin: Master of Syougi
SNK vs. Capcom: SVC Chaos
desc: SVC Chaos is a fighting game that features characters from SNK and Capcom franchises, who are locked in a war between Order and Chaos to decide the fate of the universe in a post-apocalyptic future.

name: Super Baseball 2020
desc: 2020 Super Baseball is a futuristic baseball game that features robots, cyborgs, and humans competing in a high tech sport in a stadium with special features and rules.

name: The King of Fighters '98: The Slugfest
The King of Fighters '99: Millennium Battle
The King of Fighters 2002: Challenge to Ultimate Battle
The King of Fighters 2003
desc: 24 selectable characters in fixed teams of three clash to defeat Rugal Bernstein.

name: The Last Blade
desc: The Last Blade is a fighting game set in the late Tokugawa shogunate era in Japan, where warriors with various weapons and fighting styles must face the threat of Death, who has been unleashed by a mysterious portal.

name: Waku Waku 7
desc: Waku Waku 7 is a fighting game where seven quirky characters, each possessing a magical Waku Waku ball, battle each other to collect all the balls and have their wish granted by a fairy.
